   <text>
      <div facs="#eSc_textblock_eb938c75" type="illustration">
        <figure>
            <desc>
                Walter Giesiking sitting at the piano.
            </desc>
        </figure>
      </div>
      <div facs="#eSc_textblock_778d31fa">
         <lb/>
            <hi rendition="#larger">
                <persName type="artist" corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/118694820">WALTER GIESEKING</persName>
            </hi>
        </div>
      <div facs="#eSc_textblock_98250902">
         <lb/>The phenomenal success of this artist recently at his first concert here con-
         <lb/>firmed the fame that preceded him from abroad.
         <seg ana="#immediate_recognizability" resp="#np" type="topic">
            His expectant <placeName>New York</placeName>
            <lb/>audience at once recognized his native genius, genuine musicianship, and
            <lb/>brilliant command of the piano.
         </seg> Impressed with
         <seg ana="#exact_reproduction" resp="#np" type="topic">
            the accuracy and perfection
            <lb/>of the first recordings of his playing by <name type="brand">Welte Mignon
            <hi rendition="#i">Licensee</hi></name>
         </seg>, for which
         <lb/>he records exclusively, he said:
         <quote>
            "The reproduction of my playing on the
            <lb/><name type="brand">Welte Mignon <hi rendition="#i">Licensee</hi></name>
            is by far the most complete and the truest that I
            <lb/>have yet heard, and surpasses by far all my anxiously awaited expectations.
            <lb/>I am filled with truly unbiased admiration."
         </quote>
        </div>
      <div facs="#eSc_textblock_aea977b8">
         <lb/>
         <hi rendition="#c">
            You may select the <name type="brand">Welte-Mignon Licensee</name> in 115 Makes of Pianos
            <lb/>A Most Interesting Art Brochure Is Yours for the Asking
         </hi>
      </div>
